data.description: Located in the desirable Sims Manor Subdivision with Warrensburg-Latham Schools.  This house is perfect for entertaining and the growing family.  You can enjoy the warm weather with an above ground pool and the cooler months with the fireplace in the Family Room.  Pool was added in 2015 and new roof in 2022.  The basement has french drains and part of the unfinished been ruffed in for an additional bath and the drywall is there to put up. Sellers will consider giving credit for deck repair.
